title: Bagged a 'chauka', sixer on the way: Minister ahead of Himachal, Gujarat polls - Hindustan Times
content: Bagged a 'chauka', sixer on the way: Minister ahead of Himachal, Gujarat polls  Hindustan TimesView Full coverage on Google News
description: The union minister also took the opportunity to attack the Aam Aadmi Party (AAP) which is seeking to expand its base in the hill state after registering a massive victory in Punjab to add to its recent dominance in Delhi polls.
